.3</span> 标题：升（choinix）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：χοῖνιξ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：choinix)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:6\">REV 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:6\">REV 6:6</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:6\">REV 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:6\">REV 6:6</a> ：<em>choinix</em> 约等于一升或一夸脱，可以不必更改数值而直接替换。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
